data.description:
This home, in Adams Lake, offers a nice family atmosphere. The front yard has a beautiful old tree and well maintained lawn.  A beautiful front door with beveled glass insert, opens to a welcoming open area and a split floor design  for privacy of the bedrooms. You would love to have breakfast or lunch around the bar in the kitchen, or enjoy any meal with family and friend around the table in the eating area.   
A double door on the hallway opens to a large master bedroom. The master bathroom has a garden tub, and separate shower. 
The back yard is partially fenced. The  patio on the back offers a good place for a grill and some chairs and table so you can enjoy the outdoors. This house is a must see property.
